Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:04.00,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a memory that I have concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:09.47,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was actually something I didn't realize I had concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.15,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:16.48,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a book on magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.53,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,This corner is the magic books section, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:24.04,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this really the best way to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.11,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to go through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.88,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we have to work hard to find a way to get everyone back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.43,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to do it for our beloved Negi-kun as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.00,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:40.96,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it might be that it was a feeling that I didn't realize before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:44.92,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's probably because I didn't want to admit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:49.58,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,You should move up further Yue; you can get more of the books that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.18,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that feeling was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:53.99,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.91,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Yue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:08.13,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.98,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an emotion that affected Yue's heart. That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.48,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,By Takahata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.03,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,By Chamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.77,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.98,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me sleep a bit longer, Chachamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.78,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.80,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem, master. Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.38,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this, Chachamaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.65,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,It was already like this by the time my system turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.85,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been transported to the magic world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:33.46,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,To be brought all the way here, that bastard Takamichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.63,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chachamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.17,N_Spells-Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,La {\1a&ff&\3a&ff&\4a&ff&}Lac Spiritus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:35.67,N_Spells-Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,La Lac {\1a&ff&\3a&ff&\4a&ff&}Spiritus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:36.52,N_Spells-Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,La Lac Spiritus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.90,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be done, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:49.75,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to your condition you have yet to fully recover your magic powers, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.39,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic can't be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.66,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.29,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Chachamaru, I'll stay. You fly out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.32,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,I deeply apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:02.39,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to recharge. I won't be able to fly for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.37,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.22,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,That we're stuck here for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.63,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.41,N_Man,,0000,0000,0000,,5 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.55,N_Zaz,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.51,N_Man,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:20.99,N_Man,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this feeling I should go rescue a survivor... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.40,N_Zaz,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:24.82,N_Zaz,,0000,0000,0000,,5 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.52,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,The trial is next Wednesday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.58,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.02,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.52,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good that Negi-kun was there in time to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.42,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually ashamed of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.98,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry home and read through this material.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.02,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.84,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.36,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I hurt my arm earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.65,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Yue-Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.13,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine- this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.30,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me carry it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.47,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.51,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:05.07,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, why don't you have Ako-san look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.66,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.18,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.75,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? N-No, it's not that I like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.18,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.02,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been like that lately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:17.75,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.79,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of juice is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.59,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is "karei" flavored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.30,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.30,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Curry = "kare-"/"karee"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.35,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,Jou-chan, lemme take a sip of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.38,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it taste like, Chamo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.58,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't quite explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.59,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to give it a try, Aniki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.15,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.57,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this flavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.96,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize the taste, but I can't recall the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.82,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: As noted earlier, Curry = "kare-"/"karee", but spicy = "karai," which, when said informally (as in, in the guy-ish manner), is pronounced "kare-"/"karee".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.82,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,For curry, it doesn't taste spicy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.32,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.65,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say "kare-" as in "curry".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.74,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant "karei," as in "flounder".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.41,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.73,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese culture is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.84,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have fish juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.41,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's even part of Japanese culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.39,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.27,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.63,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.30,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,You're head-over-heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.42,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now you are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.48,N_FF,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are different when you look at Negi-chan, mya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.70,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:22.06,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any particular feelings towards Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.06,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, that straw...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.49,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,... is an indirect kiss with Negi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.15,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-Indirect kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:36.33,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call an indirect kiss a smooch on the elbow or on the knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.49,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indirect... kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.48,N_Shic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing you should be embarrassed about, mya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:47.80,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a flat-out direct kiss with him when you made a provisional contract with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.83,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I had no choice when that happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.63,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides I wasn't the only one; everyone else in class did it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.32,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:04.83,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that the class kissed was not Negi-san, but a Chupacabra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:10.44,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he was in human form, you personally kissed him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:14.55,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you were the last person to kiss him when he was in his human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.45,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,In a good way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.30,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a good way!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.54,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,From that time on, and above all else,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.75,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.59,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,In love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.00,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.81,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a good way…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.42,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.80,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Jui...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.80,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: "Koi" means "carp", but it can also mean "love".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.72,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I feel about Negi-sensei... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.72,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Garfish in Japanese is said "kisu", but that can also mean "kiss". Hence the "kiss me" pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.20,N_Yuu,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out! I got a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.21,N_Yuu,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we do sukiyaki tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.64,N_Ako,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuna, you really like green onions don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:47.85,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Green onions = "negi"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:47.85,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like green onions!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.77,N_Kaz,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think it’s a bit chilly today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.48,N_Say,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Maybe I should wear some more layers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.87,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: wearing layers of clothing = "kasanegi"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.87,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear more layers... !!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.61,N_Nat,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-nee, what are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.05,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Tchaikovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:03.45,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a recording by the New York Philaharmonic Orchestra in Carnegie Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.99,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,CarNEGIe Hall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.35,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.55,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get nervous whenever I hear anything related to Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.44,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try this one out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.92,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamoto no Yoshitsune...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.92,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: A popular figure in Japanese myth/lore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.46,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Night on the Galactic Railroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.46,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: A famous classic novel by Kenji Miyazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.57,N_Shic,,0000,0000,0000,,What was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.16,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamoto no Yoshitsu{\b1}NE-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.29,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: These are the Japanese pronunciations of the two lines. (Can you see the emphasis?)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.29,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}GI{\b0}nga tetsudou no yoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.02,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez! {\1a&ff&\3a&ff&\4a&ff&}Desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:32.84,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez! {\r0}Desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.11,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.44,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.73,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally calmed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.28,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.01,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I hiding like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.54,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm going to do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.72,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.01,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something about this in the materials I read last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:06.01,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the legend, with this you are able to evade tricks from evil fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:12.81,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This would be perfect to give to Negi-sensei to protect him from evil fairies or other creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.04,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.61,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is pounding like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.79,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.41,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.39,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.38,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Today you promised you were going to help us capture the Bonge Bonge didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.68,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.16,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:37.79,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna, when you say that, aren't you just volunteering people to help without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:41.91,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, if he didn't refuse, isn't it the same as promising to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.14,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,Another heavy-handed move, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.09,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was looking all over for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.77,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you got caught up in something bad, so we were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.69,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.36,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.21,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,because we're all alive and kickin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.70,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Negi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.98,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This protective charm is for you, Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.45,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Thank you very much, Yue-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.55,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.81,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a hand when you're done with lunch, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.72,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.61,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei is alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.45,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.46,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what should I say if I want to give it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.93,N_FF,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.99,N_Kae,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were out walking around, we came across some beautiful flowers, de gozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.70,N_FF,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they're cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.90,N_FF,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought this for you, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.90,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.19,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.95,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give it to him if I do it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.78,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.16,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a fresh batch of steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.74,N_Sat,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.45,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.83,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy; help yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.58,N_Kuu,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you were, Negi-bozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.04,N_Kuu,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you help me with some techniques, aru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.39,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah! W-Wait a minute, Kuu Fei-san... !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.96,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.73,N_Mis,,0000,0000,0000,,We made ourselves a new cheerleading uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.51,N_Sak,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.02,N_Mad,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Negi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.23,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,You all look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.56,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.24,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun's rather popular isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:26.20,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets pretty hard when you've got so many rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.12,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling them "rivals" is kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.04,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's none of my business if people want to be friendly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.46,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,with Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.27,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? That's pretty heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.76,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be mean if we didn't cheer Nodoka on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.79,N_Har,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Negi-kun is so popular, it puts Nodoka in a bit of a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.53,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.77,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.71,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka's got her eyes set on Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.48,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka is my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.38,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.82,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't be falling for Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.83,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's a ramen place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.75,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.36,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.95,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.91,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me to ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:27.32,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna eat with Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:30.14,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that makes me feel warm and fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.69,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll get whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.23,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.68,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,2 bowls of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.64,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice place you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.28,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.29,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.05,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.12,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,How's school been for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.03,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Been able to make friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.03,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:54.60,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? If you get bullied, let Daddy know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.08,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Thank you, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:58.75,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.86,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.98,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.41,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.22,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.92,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.31,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.32,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shobon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.34,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:23.86,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shobon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.58,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.03,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shobon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.93,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.73,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shobon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:32.64,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.54,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shobon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.12,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.94,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: These are sound effects of her powering down, and the sound of a plug... being plugged in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.79,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather interesting aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.28,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:48.92,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.68,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.01,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't cormorant fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.02,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Cormorant fishing = method of fishing involving use of a cormorant bird to catch fish which is then reeled back so the fisherman can grab the bird's catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.51,N_Hak,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the set of profiles the bad guys had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.72,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find something similar between them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.24,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,we can figure out why they are after these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.81,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede-san was first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.48,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yuuna-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.78,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Chiu-Chiu-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.82,N_Chi,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Chiu-Chiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:17.19,N_Hak,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did an analysis and other than being in the same year,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.04,N_Hak,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no real connection between everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:24.41,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.09,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,The names fit together like shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:31.18,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Shiritori = Japanese children's game where you have to take the last kana in a word to make another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.78,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiritori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.19,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.31,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma"na",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:33.30,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,"Na"tsu"mi",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.81,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi"yaki"e",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:36.40,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: She's misconstruing it, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.40,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,"E"incho
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.52,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's a riddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.91,N_Chi,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.24,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my name isn't even Eincho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.84,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,Since its in England, it's in English...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.53,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,How about angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.53,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: Angel = "einjoru" (she's making the "ru" pretty silent)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.72,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yukihiro Ayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.52,N_Hak,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a word like Eincho in English anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.53,N_Chi,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither is Miyakie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.92,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:01.82,N_Nab,,0000,0000,0000,,At least Natsumi should be swapped with Makie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.46,N_Nat,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's a text from Chizu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.76,N_Nat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.11,N_Nat,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.01,N_Sat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.18,N_Sat,,0000,0000,0000,,Murakami Natsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.58,N_Nat,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.46,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka is my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.61,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka likes Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:29.96,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I probably just like him because Nodoka likes him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.78,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.57,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit tough to read through all this, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.37,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, I'm sorry Yue-Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.96,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,I zoned out, so I missed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.87,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.17,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:50.63,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't exactly have a reason to like him like Nodoka does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.11,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.88,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Yue-Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.14,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.56,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka, why is it that you like Negi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.43,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? "W-why," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:08.36,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei is cute, honest, smart, and he can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:13.34,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm older than him, he is so mature and, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.28,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:14.95,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.15,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.08,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.84,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is someone that you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.09,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to have a reason to like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.72,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,My gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:31.16,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without a reason, I do like Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.68,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.22,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:40.46,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that mean that it would be fine for me to like Negi-sensei as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.96,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-Yue, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.77,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:49.63,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting weird lately. Is there something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.04,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.95,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-Yue, we're best friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:59.62,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about anything. You know I'm always here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.25,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:02.66,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.18,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you, Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.04,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.87,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-Yue... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.89,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:19.68,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I such an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:24.64,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to hurt my best friend, but still I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.26,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.55,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,The patient is a 15 year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.31,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,She was found collapsed in a corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.46,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitals are 54, 31.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.14,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.39,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,is now 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.44,N_Mis,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to take a blood count, analyze her biochemistry, blood agents, and urinalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:48.10,N_Mis,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I need a CT on her abdomen and all directional photographs of her cervical vertebrae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.81,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.46,N_Mis,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:53.84,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,World...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:54.92,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,delicacies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:55.68,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,-noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.76,N_Aki,,0000,0000,0000,,The other patient is showing the same abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.24,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.01,N_Mots,,0000,0000,0000,,how are my vitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.13,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.04,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.06,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekane-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.69,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.15,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you can tell someone, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.24,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,That's painful to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:26.65,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more painful when it’s a secret you can't even share with someone important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:31.42,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekane-san, do you have a painful secret that you keep inside you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.02,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:36.85,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you would be able to understand my pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.43,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,"The king has donkey ears."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.44,N_Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Note: This is a phrase based on the story of King Midas when he angered the dogs and gets donkey ears for his troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.44,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:48.23,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,In that story, in the end everyone laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.67,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,But if no one laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.79,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,if you yelled out loud, wouldn't that be refreshing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.53,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.39,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.53,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will hear you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:03.81,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.54,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.17,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.32,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I come here sometimes to shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.09,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.54,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.08,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.68,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.72,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,... I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.50,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.30,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... like Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.86,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.61,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.52,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.26,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.73,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.98,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says, I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:00.56,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:14.93,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.58,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,The batteries have been recharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.43,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.50,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not fully recharged, so I cannot take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.64,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will go seek help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.76,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,No other way, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.90,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.28,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.73,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.90,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about what happened earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.21,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Well... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:44.77,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when I am in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.34,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-Yue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.37,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.06,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.93,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:58.36,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly this makes you immune to fairy trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:02.48,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka, give this to Negi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.58,N_Nod,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to give... to Negi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:09.34,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should increase the good feelings between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.58,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, that memory will be kept hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.18,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,This pure memory is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:20.91,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-{\1a&ff&\3a&ff&\4a&ff&}cr-et.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:21.53,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-cr{\1a&ff&\3a&ff&\4a&ff&}-et.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.25,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-cr-et.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:27.00,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, we continue on with the attempts to halt the situation in the magic world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.97,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:05.58,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,The steamed bun was first invented by Zhuge Liang during the Three Kingdoms period.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:08.55,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,During a rough storm that kept him from crossing a river,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.14,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,he threw nikuman into the raging waters and was able to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:11.74,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the steamed bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:16.34,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time... "Aiya? It seems like something is going to happen!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:19.39,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,"This may surely bring an end to the world!" by Lingshen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.17,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Will this be the nikuman's debut appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:24.92,N_Lin,,0000,0000,0000,,Achou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.23,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:29.06,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Is help on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:29.66,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:31.23,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.28,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the reason you went?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:36.01,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I came back with supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.78,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:40.73,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever, I'm starving. Hand that over!
